high_descs: Walk forward, turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the butter knife in the back of the cabbage.
Step back to be center with the table.
Slice the cabbage on the table.
Stand the knife blade up on the handle of the spoon.
Pick up a slice of cabbage.
Turn right, step forward, turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the cabbage on the second to top shelf, close the door.  Wait a few seconds and then remove the cabbage from the fridge.
Turn left, walk forward, turn left, walk to the wall, turn right to be at the edge of the sink.
Place the cabbage slice in the left corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a slice of cabbage in the fridge, place in the sink afterwards.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen table.
Look down to face the lettuce on the table.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Place the knife on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the table.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the lettuce slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn left and step forward to face the sink.
Place the lettuce slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cool a lettuce slice plus place it in the sink.

high_descs: Go to the left of the table
Grab the knife off of the table
Look down at the table
Slice the lettuce on the table
Put the knife on the table
Grab a slice of the lettuce
Turn around and go to the fridge
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and then take it out
Turn around and go to the sink
Put the lettuce in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting cold sliced lettuce in the sink
